<l>maṟappi ṉevaṉāvaṉ maṟkoṉ maṟappaṟiyē </l>
<l>ṉuḷḷiṉu muḷḷañ cuṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have never forgotten (the pleasure); even to think of it burns my soul; could I live, if I should ever forget it ?</l>
